726456f-b.text:
1071-1087 Cypress Ave. (foreground), at and adjoining the N.E. corner (left) of Summerfield Ave., showing in the foreground the Rothjen farmhouse which was demolished prior to 1927. Harding Court, a 4-story apartment house, now occupies the site. This is a set of
two views.
April 1925.
View 21 January 1924.
Eumene L. Armbruster Collection.
